  "detailed_description": "<strong>DelayedSun</strong> is a third-person shooter survival horror game set in a post-apocalyptic world filled with flesh-hungry zombies.<br><br>Melvin has to rescue his kidnapped friend, Elisa.<br>Elisa has been kidnapped by crazy scientists on a remote island. Will Melvin survive his long journey?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1197730/extras/43e97ef0c5287fa9fb15fd2ba67b7e9a.poster.avif?t=1689058641\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1197730/extras/43e97ef0c5287fa9fb15fd2ba67b7e9a.webm?t=1689058641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1197730/extras/43e97ef0c5287fa9fb15fd2ba67b7e9a.mp4?t=1689058641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features :</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">• Immersive Gameplay</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">• Realistic Combat Experience</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">• Realistic Environments</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">• Inventory, Crafting & Skill Tree</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">• Stunning Mission & Storyline</ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WILL YOU SURVIVE?</h2>Can Melvin survive and bring Elisa alive?",
